Beeil dich.

00:22:38.887 --> 00:22:39.647
Schwerer.

00:22:43.448 --> 00:22:44.087
Pangzi!

00:22:50.968 --> 00:22:51.807
Pan Zi.

00:22:52.167 --> 00:22:52.928
Pan Zi.

